# OCMI Mini Timesheets — Cursor rules

Ver también: SPEC.md, CURSOR.MD

## Stack
- pnpm monorepo: `apps/api`, `apps/web`, `packages/shared` (`@mini-timesheets/shared`)
- API: Hono + Drizzle + PostgreSQL
- Web: Next.js 15 + React Query + Tailwind

## Conventions
- Overtime/pay only in `packages/shared` (`calculateWeeklyPay`, `getWeekStart`)
- Shared Zod schemas for API + client validation (`schemas.ts`)
- API errors: `{ error: { code, message } }` + `Accept-Language` (en/es)
- Employees soft-deleted via `deactivatedAt`
- Weekly approval (`weekly_approvals`) locks time entries for that employee/week
- Payroll week: Sunday → Saturday (US)

## Do not
- Put business logic in React components or API route handlers
- Hard-delete employees
- Allow time entry mutations when week is approved
- Use `deletedAt` on time entries (not in this design)
